secondary_street_name: And North East Of Victory Park,
description: Reserved matters application pursuant to Conditions B1, B8, Q1 and Q4 of the Stratford City Outline Planning Permission (ref: 10/90641/EXTODA) relating to the details of layout, scale, design, appearance, access and landscaping of Plot N08. Comprising the construction of buildings up to a maximum height of G+30 storeys providing 481 residential units, complementary retail (use classes A1-A5) and leisure (use class D1/D2), along with associated landscaping. This application also seeks approval in writing, to exceed maximum parameter heights shown in parameter plan (7) and as indicated within the Zonal Masterplan for Zones 3-6, pursuant to conditions A4 and D9/D9A of the outline planning permission.
